item.title: About me
item.description: My name is Danyang Zhang, I go by Jasmine as well. I am originally from Zhengzhou, Henan, China. I am currently a first-year Ph.D. student at the Department of Statistics in Iowa State University. Before joining ISU, I completed my B.S. in Statistics at Beijing Normal Univerity and my M.S. in Business Analytics at University of Texas at Austin. I enjoy cooking, baking, working out, hiking and traveling in my spare time!
